issue.title: POST to question returns invalid JSON
issue.body:
I haven't had much time to look into it but it seems like the POST to /question is returning invalid JSON which causes the buttons to be unresponsive.
This may be related to the broken init_tweets() and parts of random_real_tweet() which I commented out for the time being...

issue.title: Game doesn't end on game over
issue.body: You can keep clicking the real/fake buttons and increasing your score, even after running out of hearts.

issue.title: Scoreboard username entry should only appear on game over
issue.body: Right now the scoreboard username entry field and submission button appear throughout the entire game but should only appear on game over.
